{
  "texts": [
    "IoTIoT aims to connect all things, such as various devices, vehicles, and sensors, via the Internet and facilitate the efficient exchange of information among them [147].",
    "Integrating ISAC into IoT devices not only achieves an intelligent connection, but also facilitates accurate environment sensing, enabling various emerging applications [12].",
    "Specifically, the sensing capability of IoT nodes enables them to intelligently connect with nearby nodes, which is crucial to enhancing the network-level sensing performance.",
    "As a result, the ISAC-enabled IoT has a wide range of applications, such as human activity detection [148] and precise positioning [11].",
    "Key ISAC techniquesThis section provides an overview of the key ISAC techniques."
  ]
}